of their site, dedicated to bringing community-driven news. Today ManageWP launches ManageWP.org, a new interactive site where anyone can share, vote and promote high quality WordPress news. The site was built with an author ranking algo [&hellip;]\'>WPTavern: ManageWP Launches Community-Curated WordPress News Site</a></li></ul></div>','no');
