s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1432:\"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www2.gotomeeting.com/register/750430618\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19840\" alt=\"3product-types-email copy\" src=\"http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/3product-types-email-copy1.png\" width=\"470\" height=\"190\" /></a></p>\n<p>iThemes Exchange has two new amazingly powerful add-ons: <a href=\"http://ithemes.com/2013/10/09/start-a-membership-site-with-ithemes-exchange/\">Membership</a> and <a href=\"http://ithemes.com/2013/10/09/sell-your-physical-products-plus-add-shipping-with-ithemes-exchange/\" target=\"_blank\">Simple Shipping</a>. With these new add-ons, Exchange now has the ability to handle physical products with shipping capabilities, plus membership content protection with built-in drip-content protection.</p>\n<p>Join us for a walkthrough webinar as we demonstrate the ease-of-use of Exchange for WordPress, Monday, Oct. 14 @ 3pm CDT</p>\n<div class=\"content-callout green\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Exchange Add-on Walkthrough &#8211; Shipping and Membership</strong><br />\nMonday, Oct. 14<br />\n3pm CDT</div>\n<p><a class=\"btn blue\" href=\"https://www2.gotomeeting.com/register/750430618\">Register for the webinar</a></p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">Can&#8217;t make the live webinar? We&#8217;ll post the recording to the blog. Follow <a href=\"http://twitter.com/ithemes\" target=\"_blank\">@iThemes</a> and we&#8217;ll keep you posted.</h6>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"http://ithemes.com/2013/10/10/exchange-simple-shipping-membership-add-on-webinar-oct-14/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\"